data.description: Discover refinement in Historic Freemason with this meticulously upgraded gem. Featuring fresh paint, a new sink, upgraded hardware, garbage disposal, and a water treatment system, every detail has been thoughtfully attended to. Enjoy the convenience of all-new appliances, including a washer and dryer, along with upgraded light fixtures, a new water heater, and plush bedroom carpeting.HOA benefits include coverage for master insurance policy, flood insurance, and water/sewer/trash services, with electric bills averaging less than $100 per month. Immerse yourself in a community predominantly occupied by veterans, fostering a welcoming environment.Furniture and decor are available for purchase. Don't miss your chance to experience elegant minimalist living. Schedule your viewing today!
